{"about_the_game":"FFF is a funny game about friendship, family, and fun. You are a newly elected space emperor, and your goal is to make everyone your friend. Even if they don't want to be. You will travel through the vast expanse of space, spreading your kindness to anyone you cross to become the most loved ruler that ever lived.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139620/extras/ascend.gif?t=1686670053\" /><br><br>Everything in this game is entirely fictional and made up, not based on actual events or people. Due to poor content and ugly art style, the game should not be played by anyone\u2026 Maybe except you. You are special.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139620/extras/gameplay_1.gif?t=1686670053\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Featuring:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Friends - many aliens and characters to meet<br></li><li>Fun - a humorous story with over-the-top dialogues<br></li><li>Family - blood is thicker than water<br></li><li>Foes - haters, influencers, devils, crypto gurus, and game reviewers</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139620/extras/gameplay_2.gif?t=1686670053\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Free updates</h2>We want to expand our universe with frequent content updates to make the game even more fun and challenging.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139620/extras/gameplay_3.gif?t=1686670053\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Besties 4Ever","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2139620/b9b6dbafef0353d7f82490ab5c41a7a3e99dc134.jpg"},{"name":"Little Helper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2139620/0282e057d27398d9b12d28e34cbb34c46bd917f0.jpg"},{"name":"Three's a crowd","path":"https://cdn.akamai